---
import HeaderFooterLayout from '../../../layouts/header-footer-layout.astro';
import { Container, Row, Col } from '../../../components/grid';
import Heading from '../../../components/heading';
import Section from '../../../components/section';
import Stack from '../../../components/stack';
import Anchor from '../../../components/anchor';
import Paragraph from '../../../components/paragraph';
---

<HeaderFooterLayout
	title="Website & Web Application Privacy Policy - Budget Warden"
	description="Privacy policy for the Budget Warden website and web application"
>
	<Section>
		<Container>
      <article>
        <Stack gap="md">
          <header>
            <Stack gap="md">
              <Heading level="h1" size={40}>Privacy Policy</Heading>
              <Heading level="h2" size={32}>Website & Web Application</Heading>
              <Stack gap="sm">
                <Paragraph>Effective Date: July 30, 2025</Paragraph>
                <Paragraph>Last Updated: July 30, 2025</Paragraph>
              </Stack>
            </Stack>
          </header>

          <Stack gap="xs">
            <Paragraph>This Privacy Policy applies to the web platforms of Budget Warden, including:</Paragraph>

            <ul>
              <li>The marketing website at https://budgetwarden.com (“Website”)</li>
              <li>The web application at https://app.budgetwarden.com (“Web App”)</li>
            </ul>
          </Stack>

          <Paragraph>These services are operated by Nikola Nikolov Lazarov ("Service Provider", "we", "us", "our").</Paragraph>

          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Information Collection and Use</Heading>

          <Heading level="h4" size={28}>On the Website (https://budgetwarden.com)</Heading>

          <Paragraph>We do not collect any personal information.</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>We use <a href="https://www.goatcounter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GoatCounter</a> to gather anonymous, cookie-less visit analytics. No personal data or cookies are used.</Paragraph>

          <Heading level="h4" size={28}>On the Web App (https://app.budgetwarden.com) and Mobile App</Heading>

          <Stack gap="xs">
            <Paragraph>When you create an account or use the service, we may collect:</Paragraph>

            <ul>
              <li>Email address</li>
              <li>First and last name</li>
              <li>Country</li>
            </ul>
          </Stack>


          <Stack gap="xs">
            <Paragraph>This data is required to:</Paragraph>

            <ul>
              <li>Register and manage your account</li>
              <li>Identify you as a user</li>
              <li>Communicate service-related updates</li>
            </ul>
          </Stack>

          <Paragraph>We <storng>do not</strong> collect location data, and we <strong>do not</strong> track users for advertising or profiling.</Paragraph>

          <Stack gap="xs">
            <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Storage and Session Management</Heading>

            <ul>
              <li>We use strictly necessary cookies in the Web App to store your login token and user data for session continuity.</li>
              <li>We may also use sessionStorage or localStorage within your browser to maintain state during your session.</li>
            </ul>
          </Stack>

          <Paragraph>All data storage is limited to purposes essential to the functionality of the application.</Paragraph>

          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Data Sharing and Third Parties</Heading>

          <Paragraph>We do not share your personal data with third parties for advertising or marketing.</Paragraph>

          <Stack gap="xs">
            <Paragraph>We may also disclose personal data:</Paragraph>

            <ul>
              <li>To comply with legal obligations or court orders</li>
              <li>To investigate fraud or abuse</li>
              <li>To trusted service providers working on our behalf under strict confidentiality terms</li>
            </ul>
          </Stack>

          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Data Retention</Heading>

          <Paragraph>We retain user data:</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>For as long as your account is active</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>For a reasonable time afterward, to support service continuity and legal compliance</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting: <a href="mailto:nikola.n.lazarov@outlook.com">nikola.n.lazarov@outlook.com</a></Paragraph>

          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Children’s Privacy</Heading>

          <Paragraph>Our services are not intended for children under 13.</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>We do not knowingly collect data from children.</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>If you believe a child has submitted personal data, please contact us immediately to remove it.</Paragraph>

          <Paragraph>In accordance with GDPR, users must be at least 16 years old to consent to data processing, unless a parent or guardian provides consent on their behalf.</Paragraph>

          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Security</Heading>

          <Paragraph>We use industry-standard physical, technical, and administrative measures to safeguard your data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</Paragraph>


          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Your Rights</Heading>

          <Stack gap="xs">
            <Paragraph>You have the right to:</Paragraph>

            <ul>
              <li>Access your data</li>
              <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
              <li>Delete your data</li>
              <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
            </ul>
          </Stack>
              
          <Paragraph>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:nikola.n.lazarov@outlook.com">nikola.n.lazarov@outlook.com</a></Paragraph>

          <Heading level="h3" size={30}>Contact Us</Heading>

          <Paragraph>If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the website or web application, or have questions about the practices, please contact the Service Provider via email at <Anchor href="mailto:nikola.n.lazarov@outlook.com">nikola.n.lazarov@outlook.com</Anchor>.</Paragraph>
			  </Stack>
      </article>
		</Container>
	</Section>
</HeaderFooterLayout>
